title: New developments in Gabby Petito case
author: 23 ABC News | KERO
description: The mystery surrounding Gabby Petito continues to grow. She's the 22-year-old woman who was last seen on a road trip with her boyfriend, who is now missing. There are several developments including what a search warrant turned up and what a park ranger in Utah saw just before Gabby's disappearance.
